description:
&lt;p&gt;The Simply Serve Ltd Procurement Team are looking to recruit a Senior Procurement Project Officer.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will be expected to work weekdays, Monday to Thursday 8:30am - 5pm, Friday 8:30am - 4:30pm. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Key activities include working closely with Procurement Officers and Senior Contracts Managers to facilitate and manage projects and contracts for client organisations in order to drive efficiencies whilst complying with the relevant legislation/policies. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder must be enthusiastic, able to communicate effectively to both internal and external providers and have a great team ethic. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you would like to seek further information or to discuss the role in general please contact Dirk Williamson, Senior Contracts Manager on 01935 383026.&lt;/p&gt;
